=====================
Rickety Bridge
=====================
Different people need different time to cross the bridge. For example, there are 4 people, 
A 1min, B 2min, C 7min, D 10min.
Use a graph to represent the state (who is where and torch is where)

=====================
Broken Car
=====================
Your car is broken. It can only go straight or turn left.
1) Shortest path
2) Least turns